Name: pyastro
Version: 1.0
Summary: Astronomical Library
Home-page: http://www.paulgriffiths.net/program/python/pyastro.php
Author: Paul Griffiths
Author-email: mail@paulgriffiths.net
License: GNU General Public License version 3
Description: An astronomical library. Contains classes for the major planetary bodies enabling the right ascension, declination, distance from earth, and zodiac sign to be calculated. Also contains functions for solving Kepler's equation, transforming rectangular to spherical coordinates, and calculating Julian dates.
Platform: UNKNOWN
